<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的家鄉啊，<delay20 />
其實就是<delay8 />人家口中所謂的<delay8 />鄉下啦。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />話說我有個死黨<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="Cheering" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />說什麼「我討厭這種鄉下！<delay8 />我要當演員！」<delay20 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />
<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然後，<delay20 />就離開家鄉了。<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然她最近的確是越來越走紅，<delay20 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但聽說她演得最好的角色<delay8 />竟然是鄉下女孩！<delay40 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣……<delay20 />她真的滿意嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的家鄉<delay8 />是個好地方，
那裡都是些好相處的傢伙喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過……<delay8 />就是空曠得很啦，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就算在自己家附近散步，<delay8 />
也很難碰到人哩。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />相較之下，<tag a="110" b="33" />就好多了，<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />走沒幾步就能碰到死黨喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="001_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的家鄉……<delay8 />實在超～級鄉下的，
根本什麼都沒有耶。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay8 /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我在那邊真的過得很開心喔！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像是跟死黨一起翹課閒聊，<delay8 />
或是在空地放煙火……<pageBreak /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就連老是<delay8 />被附近的老太太怒罵，<delay8 />
也都是很棒的回憶喔！<delay40 />
<size value="75" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過老太太還真是可怕啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<size value="100" /></message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="010_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />前陣子<delay8 />我不小心忘了幫花澆水，<delay20 />
結果讓我寶貝的花枯萎了……<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="SadSpiral" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且那還是我生日時，<delay8 />死黨送的花！<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我真的<delay8 />超受打擊的<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />心裡還責備自己，<delay8 />
為什麼沒有好好照顧它啊！？<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過呢，<delay8 />我仔細看看枯萎的花<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />才發現！<delay20 />花竟然留下了種子！<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以這次<delay8 />我一定會好好照顧它的！<delay20 />
賭上我<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 /><tag a="110" b="10" />之名！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不久前，<delay8 />我不小心讓我寶貝的花枯萎啦！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明明前一天<delay8 />都還開得那麼漂亮……<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過啊，<delay8 />我查了很多資料，
又幫它澆水，<delay8 />又幫它修剪枝葉……<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />結果新的花朵<delay8 />又開出來啦！<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以要是你的花枯萎了，<delay20 />
也別馬上放棄，<delay8 />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />把所有能試的方法<delay8 />都試一遍吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不久前，<delay8 />我因為一時偷懶沒好好照顧，<delay20 />
害自己用心栽種的花差點枯萎了……<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Oops" target="actor" targetSpec="" />當時我腦袋裡<delay8 />都變得一片空白啦！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過呢，<delay8 />我沒有放棄，繼續照料它，<delay20 />
結果它又<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />漸漸復活哩！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀～<delay8 />那時候<delay8 />我真的<delay20 />
見識到了<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />花朵的幹勁啊！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真慶幸<delay8 />我沒有放棄！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="020" attrib="15 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><anim id="Sleepy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我啊，<delay8 />總是一不小心<delay8 />
就會熬夜呢！</message>
	<message label="021" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="021_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />本來我想說<delay8 />得快點睡才行～<delay20 />
可是又想在睡前<delay8 />做點別的事，<delay8 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />於是就開始看起漫畫之類的！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />結果一看下去，<delay8 />就會很想知道後續的劇情吧？<delay8 />
然後手就停不下來啦！<pageBreak /><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />結果<delay8 />到最後就變成……<delay8 />既然都看到這裡了，<delay20 />
乾脆全部看完好啦！<10_4 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你懂吧？<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="0" />然後<delay8 /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />天就亮了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="021_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />每次只要我決定<delay8 />當天一定要早點睡的時候，<delay20 />
就會有死黨<delay8 />打電話過來啊。<pageBreak /><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你問我怎麼辦？<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那當然是<delay8 />
死黨的煩惱比較重要啊！<delay40 />
<size value="75" />雖然有時也會聊些沒營養的話啦<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><size value="100" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />反正<delay8 />對我來說，<delay8 />
起床這種事一點都不難！<delay20 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有幹勁無難事啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="021_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我只要半夜一戴上耳機，<delay8 />
聽起喜歡的樂團歌曲，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />情緒就會<delay8 />越來越高漲哩！<pageBreak />等我回過神來，<delay8 />才發現自己在大喊著
<anim id="Cheering" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />「呀呼～～～～～！！」<delay40 />之類的，<delay8 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />搞得像在看演唱會一樣。<pageBreak />後來還因為實在太亢奮了，<delay8 />
過了老半天都睡不著啊！<10_4 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay8 />對鄰居就有點不好意思了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="030" attrib="1f 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />前陣子我從老家那邊<delay8 />
收到了家鄉寄來的水果喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />原本我還想說<delay8 />我早就吃膩了，<delay20 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但打開箱子的瞬間，<delay8 />一股懷念的氣味飄來，<delay20 />
讓我莫名紅了眼眶啊！</message>
	<message label="031" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="031_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />下次我打算<delay8 />換我寄<tag a="110" b="7" arg="0xcd00" />回去！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是你也有重要的人，<delay8 />
不妨也寄給對方吧？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="031_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過<delay20 />我的眼淚很快就收回去了。<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一想起<delay8 />那過去的放蕩青春<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊～！<delay20 />好想忘掉！！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="031_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />人只要有個地方能回去，<delay20 />心裡就會<delay8 />有個支柱在啊～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而我能放心地過日子，<delay8 />
或許也拜此所賜吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="040" attrib="29 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />話說，<delay8 />你別看我這樣，<delay8 />
其實我可是很愛照顧小孩的！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以我也常常會<delay8 />看顧附近的小孩喔。</message>
	<message label="041" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="041_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看到那麼小的傢伙<delay8 />
每天都拼盡全力地過活，<delay20 />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就會讓我覺得<delay8 />自己也得努力才行呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />他們會帶給我幹勁，<delay20 />
真是太了不起啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="041_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然小孩總是搞得我七葷八素的，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過<delay8 />那高興時的笑臉<delay8 />
還是可愛得令人招架不住呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊～<delay20 />不過，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />整整一小時都把小孩扛在肩上<delay20 />
還真的挺要命的<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="041_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />小孩……<delay8 />一下子就會長大呢。<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然後嘴巴也越來越伶俐，<delay20 />
在一旁看著他們長大，真的很有趣！<pageBreak /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay8 />大概是害羞的關係吧，<delay20 />
他們會開始不太向我撒嬌，<delay8 />
這就讓我有點寂寞了<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="050" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="050_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我啊，<delay8 />最喜歡種花了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看到當初種下的種子成長，開出花朵時，<delay20 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我高興得<delay8 />差點都要跳起舞來了！<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過大家<delay20 />好像覺得很意外我會喜歡花。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我老家的死黨們竟然還說什麼<delay20 />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />「比起可愛的花朵，<delay20 />你比較適合食蟲植物！」<pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是的，<delay20 />島上的居民也是這麼想的嗎？<10_4 />
<anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，<delay20 />對了！<delay frames="40" />不然你就來幫我宣傳，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讓大家知道，我喜歡花朵吧！</message>
	<message label="050_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我說呀，<delay20 />這件事我一定要跟你說！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />之前<delay20 />我回老家一趟時才知道，<delay20 />
在我家鄉的死黨之間<delay8 />竟然流傳著奇怪的謠言。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好像是有人擅自亂傳，<delay20 />
說什麼我搬到這座島嶼，<delay20 />
<anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是為了跟<delay8 />無人島上的巨大生物決鬥！<pageBreak /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就算是我，碰到這種事也忍不住笑了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我家鄉的死黨們<delay20 />難道當我是<delay8 />
超人之類的<delay8 />超級英雄嗎<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="060" attrib="3d 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />挑選適合的禮物<delay20 />其實挺困難的哩。</message>
	<message label="061" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="061_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要這禮物是對方想著我挑選的，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不管收到怎麼樣的禮物，<delay8 />
我都會感到很開心喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，<delay20 />我懂了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這就是選禮物時<delay8 />最重要的一點啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="061_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然想挑選符合對方喜好的東西，<delay20 />
<anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但總覺得對方<delay8 />早就有相同的東西了<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />直接問本人雖然也是一種方法，<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我想給對方一個驚喜啊～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Oops" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真令人煩惱呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="061_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />到底要選怎麼樣的禮物，<delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />才能將我那熾熱的友情傳達出去呢？<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />熾熱<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />用超辣的<tag a="135" b="3" arg="0xcd00" /><delay20 />，
來傳達到底有多熾熱如何啊？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="070" attrib="47 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />話說我今天<delay8 />做了一個奇怪的夢喔<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="071" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="071_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我夢到我成為<tag a="135" b="6" arg="0xcd00" />的明星選手，<delay20 />
在頒獎台上接受賽後訪問<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />採訪時聽到的全是沒聽過的語言，<delay20 />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我因為完全聽不懂，所以無法回答。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />難道那些<delay20 />都是外星語言嗎？
<anim id="SadSpiral" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我是第一次接受賽後採訪，<delay8 />
所以本來有好多想說的事情呢～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感覺有點不甘心啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="071_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我夢到我寫的書變成百萬暢銷書，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而令人在意的書本標題是<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />《奇妙之島上的<tag a="110" b="15" />》！<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然<delay8 />內容沒什麼了不起的，<delay20 />
但是簽名會可是大排長龍喔。<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />即使是夢境，那也是我一生難忘的回憶啊。</message>
	<message label="071_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我夢到我成為一名<tag a="135" b="4" arg="0xcd00" />歌手，<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那天是巡迴演出的最後一天。<delay frames="40" />
當我要返場表演安可曲時<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我聽到觀眾們熱情的喝采，
胸口不禁一熱，<delay8 />眼淚奪眶而出喔。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能體驗現實中不可能發生的事，<delay8 /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我很滿足喔。</message>
	<message label="071_04" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我記得我夢到的是<tag a="135" b="3" arg="0xcd00" />的
大胃王比賽途中，<delay20 />我明明只差一口就能贏了……<delay20 />
<anim id="SadSpiral" target="actor" targetSpec="" />結果不知道為什麼，我就是無法吃下最後一口。<pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那完全就是我的幹勁不足吧。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然我到最後還是不清楚結果如何，<delay20 />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我已經決定<delay20 />要重新鍛鍊自己了喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
</msbt>